Bankinter to Cut 4 Percent of Workforce, CEO Tells Expansion

-- B y   E s t e b a n   D u a r t e
-- 
2011-09-19T06:06:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-19/bankinter-to-cut-4-percent-of-workforce-ceo-tells-expansion.html
Bankinter SA (BKT)  will cut about 4
percent of its workforce, Chief Executive Officer Maria Dolores Dancausa said in an interview with  Expansion.   The Madrid-based lender will eliminate between 300 and 350
positions, the newspaper reported, citing Dancausa.  The Bankinter CEO confirmed a target of increasing profit
this year by 20 percent over last year, Expansion said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Esteban Duarte in Madrid at 
